#X text 53 63 - "-n": make invisible initially \; - "-v [const or field name]": assign a variable to make this visible/invisible \; - "-x": disable all mouse actions \; - "-xr": disable mouse actions in run mode \; - "-xe": disable mouse actions in edit mode \; - "-e": enable single-click text selecting/editing \; - "-ne": disable all text selecting/editing., f 57;
